                  Convert your course schedule to Google Calendar
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="learn-more">
                <p class="arrow">↗︎</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </a>

          <hr class="project-hr" />

          <a class="project-link" href="project template">
            <div class="project">
              <div class="project-content">
                <p class="project-title">Spotify Adblocker</p>
                <p class="project-description">
                  A simple script to block ads in Spotify on your Mac
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="learn-more">
                <p class="arrow">↗︎</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </a>

          <hr class="project-hr" />

          <a class="project-link" href="project template">
            <div class="project">
              <div class="project-content">
                <p class="project-title">Calculator App</p>
                <p class="project-description">
                  A simple calculator app with a clean design and keyboard
                  support
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="learn-more">
                <p class="arrow">↗︎</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </a>

          <hr class="project-hr" />
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="blog-posts-section">
        <div class="blog-section-top">
          <h1 class="blog-section-title">Featured Blog Posts</h1>
          <a class="all-posts" href="blogs">
            <p>View all posts <span class="arrow">↗︎</span></p>
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="blog-posts">
          <a class="post-link" href="blog template">
            <div class="post">
              <div class="blog-content">
                <h2 class="post-title">Building my portfolio website</h2>

                <div class="published-date">
